Test cases:

1. Verify registration using a valid phone number

2. Verify registration using an invalid phone number

3. Verify that the phone number field only accepts numbers [enter abc]

4. Verify registration while using Arabic phone number

5. Verify that numbers keyboard appears when user clicks on phone number field


OTP test cases:

1. Verify while using a valid OTP

2. Verify that user can request OTP two times

3. Verify using an old OTP after requesting a new one

4. Verify that OTP is valid only for 10 minutes [test after 5 minutes - test after 12 minutes]

5. Verify testing all scenarios while changing from mobile data to wifi
